-- Fiat Agrees With Labor Unions to Proceed With Pomigliano Car Factory Plan
-- Tommaso Ebhardt
-- 2010-07-09T10:43:46Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-09/fiat-agrees-with-labor-unions-to-proceed-with-pomigliano-car-factory-plan.html

          
          
             Fiat SpA agreed today in Turin with
CISL and UIL unions to implement the accord regarding the
“production continuity” at Pomigliano plant, the Italian
company said in an e-mailed statement today.  
          
          


  


        